PermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-17-mln-vehicles-china-says-market-regulator-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称中国将加强对芬太尼化学品的监管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</link><description>白宫周二表示，中国表示将开始对三种用于制造非法芬太尼的化学品的生产加强控制和监管，称此举“向前迈出了宝贵的一步”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:34:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-beef-up-regulations-fentanyl-chemicals-white-house-says-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利的梅洛尼表示，她带女儿去中国为母亲们树立了榜样</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利总理梅洛尼表示，带七岁女儿对中国进行正式访问树立了良好榜样，有助于促进职业母亲的权利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:30:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-says-she-set-example-mothers-by-taking-daughter-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>线上券商富途、UP Fintech暂停美股夜盘交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</link><description>以帮助中国投资者购买全球股票而闻名的在线券商富途控股和UP Fintech Holding已告诉客户，在全球市场波动加剧后，美国股票的夜盘交易将于周二暂停。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/online-brokerages-futu-up-fintech-suspend-night-trading-us-stocks-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动推出 AI 视频应用程序，加入 OpenAI Sora 竞争对手行列</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</link><description>字节跳动扩大了其可根据文本提示生成视频的软件产品范围，加入了越来越多的中国科技公司的行列，进入了ChatGPT创建者OpenAI也瞄准的新兴市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-joins-openais-sora-rivals-with-ai-video-app-launch-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>Zalando 将在中国开设科技网站；目前没有进入市场的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</link><description>Zalando 周二表示，将在中国科技中心深圳开设一个新的科技网站，但目前不打算将其市场扩展到中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zalando-open-tech-site-china-no-current-plans-enter-market-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着关税的临近，记号笔制造商纽厄尔将更多业务从中国转移</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</link><description>记号笔制造商纽厄尔品牌公司（Newell Brands）首席执行官克里斯·彼得森（Chris Peterson）在接受路透社采访时表示，由于美国总统大选前面临关税的“不确定性”，纽厄尔品牌公司正在将部分厨房用具的生产迁出中国，并将其书写业务的生产迁至田纳西州。 。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sharpie-maker-newell-moves-more-operations-china-tariffs-loom-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>华为与北京汽车推出首款联合开发的电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国科技集团华为和北京汽车周二推出了首款联合开发的电动汽车（EV）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:38:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-huawei-baic-motor-launch-first-jointly-developed-ev-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>意大利消息人士称，中国东风汽车有望在意大利建汽车厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</link><description>意大利知情人士周二表示，意大利政府与中国东风汽车集团关于在意大利建设汽车工厂的谈判已进入后期阶段。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:46:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italian-govt-chinas-dongfeng-advanced-talks-over-auto-plant-italy-sources-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国城市遭遇创纪录高温，水稻种植区受到威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-limits-outdoor-lighting-record-heat-strains-grid-2024-08-06/</link><description>极端高温烘烤了中国东部沿海地区的大城市，并急剧增加了对家庭和办公室降温的电力需求，而中国内陆地区的炎热气温引发了人们对水稻作物受损的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-megacity-limits-outdoor-lighting-record-heat-strains-grid-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团第二季度表现强劲，因美国反弹超过中国疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</link><description>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团报告称，由于美国的强劲反弹抵消了中国的疲软，第二季度每间可用客房的收入增长了 3.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-posts-32-rise-revenue-per-room-q2-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>舍弗勒第二季度利润下降近30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</link><description>德国机器和汽车零部件制造商舍弗勒公司周二报告称，由于轴承和工业解决方案部门（尤其是欧洲和中国）盈利下滑，第二季度核心利润下降近30%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>